DESCRIPTION:Good morning\,\n\nPlease hold this time for July's Batten Opera
 tions Meeting. Documents for these meetings will be stored on the followin
 g Teams channel: Batten School Staff | Batten Operations Meeting<https://t
 eams.microsoft.com/l/channel/19%3A8cbcc1a004a54c32992ce2f6304f5dd5%40threa
 d.tacv2/Batten%20Operations%20Meeting?groupId=9270d3ae-84b1-4573-a06e-8ee0
 2b237630&tenantId=7b3480c7-3707-4873-8b77-e216733a65ac&ngc=true>.\n\nThe p
 urpose of this meeting is to periodically gather the functional leaders of
  the school to review current and upcoming school operational issues—esp
 ecially activities that impact multiple functional teams and/or require hi
 gh levels of coordination and collaboration. This meeting provides a forum
  to raise and resolve or at least identify next steps related to broad ope
 rating issues impacting the school.\n\nThank you\,\nSean Michael\n\n[https
 ://st2.zoom.us/static/6.3.36139/image/new/ZoomLogo_110_25.png] <https://zo
 om.com>\nHi there\,\nSean Michael Flattery is inviting you to a scheduled 
 Zoom meeting.\nJoin Zoom Meeting<https://virginia.zoom.us/j/91097144106?pw
 d=MCjg2cabTh9Xa1BZiRQciwz8pQONRZ.1&from=addon>\nOne tap mobile:\nUS: +1470
 2509358\,\,91097144106#<tel:+14702509358\,\,91097144106#> or +14703812552\
