DESCRIPTION:Hi Jennett\,\n\nThe Virginia Policy Review (VPR) asked me if I 
 could reserve the Seminar Room for their last three meetings of the semest
 er\, due to the room having more technological abilities than the student 
 lounge. Is there any chance the room would be available from 5-7pm on this
  date?\n\nThank you in advance!\n\nSincerely\,\nShawn\n
