DESCRIPTION:Good afternoon\,\n\nOn Friday\, November 7\, Academics will be 
 hosting a lunch discussion for faculty teaching in the BA core this Fall. 
 This is a chance to share what you are seeing with our students (challenge
 s\, trends\, areas of strength\, etc.). Your insights help us better align
  our services and support with student (and faculty) needs.\n\nWe hope you
  can join us for lunch and good conversation.\n\nThank you\,\n\nHeather\n\
 n
