BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Punting this to early next year as the end of the year is creep
 ing up quickly. Let me know if you want to discuss anything prior\, but I 
 think we have some time around this. Thanks for the flexibility around the
  meeting schedule.\n\n----------------------------------------------------
 --------------   \n\nAll\,\n\nPutting 90 minutes on the calendar for
  us to come together and discuss Batten's 2026 events calendar. My goal wi
 th this kickoff meeting is to align our teams on overall event strategy an
 d how that plays into the larger Batten and UVA ecosystem.\n\n\nDuring the
  meeting\, we will do look back at past years events and begin defining su
 ccess metrics.\n\nPlease come prepared to talk about what events you are p
 lanning for 2026\, what other events we could\, or should\, be doing\, and
  what events we could probably skip.\n\nKeeping the group small at first a
 nd then we can invite additional stakeholders in after one or two meetings
  together. But let me know if there is anyone who should be in this first 
 meeting. I also hope this serves as an example of how we can come together
  as cross-functional teams to align overall strategies.\nLooking forward t
 o it!\nNicki\n\n[https://st2.zoom.us/static/6.3.46712/image/new/ZoomLogo_1
 10_25.png] <https://zoom.com>\nHi there\,\nNicki Deuel is inviting you to 
 a scheduled Zoom meeting.\nJoin Zoom Meeting<https://virginia.zoom.us/j/92
 191895093?pwd=3Cc5koVlqO4dpZugzwDuAlC12Jlzsb.1&from=addon>\nOne tap mobile
 :\nUS: +16513728299\,\,92191895093#<tel:+16513728299\,\,92191895093#> or +
 17866351003\,\,92191895093#<tel:+17866351003\,\,92191895093#>\nMeeting URL
